#include <stdio.h>
#include "set.h"

int main(){
	char cmd[20];
	Set s[100];
	
	int number_bits;
	scanf("%d", &number_bits);
	
	while(scanf("%s", cmd) != EOF){
		switch(cmd[0]){
			case 'i':
				if(cmd[2] == 'i'){ //init
					int set_id;
					scanf("%d", &set_id);
					initializeSet(&s[set_id], number_bits);
				}
				else{ //intersect
					int set_id1, set_id2;
					scanf("%d%d", &set_id1, &set_id2);
					if(intersect(s[set_id1], s[set_id2]))
						printf("yes\n");
					else
						printf("no\n");
				}
				break;
			case 'a':{ //add
				int element, set_id;
				scanf("%d", &set_id);
				scanf("%d", &element);
				addElement(&s[set_id], element);
				break;
			}
			case 'r':{ //remove
				int element, set_id;
				scanf("%d", &set_id);
				scanf("%d", &element);
				removeElement(&s[set_id], element);
				break;
			}
			case 'p':{ //print
				int set_id;
				scanf("%d", &set_id);
				printSet(s[set_id]);
				return 0;
			}
				
		}
	}
}
